{
  "text": "Significant advances are also being made within academia, as pointed out by [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] , as research centers and universities worldwide are striving to advance studies on technology mobility, vehicle-infrastructure interaction, and management and business-related issues for the consolidation of autonomous vehicles.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "115843384",
